<h3 class="p1">
  <span class="s1">Our philosophy in development cooperation:</span>
</h3>
<p class="p2">
  From&nbsp;BPDE&nbsp;Foundation&nbsp;we understand that&nbsp;the actions taken by&nbsp;public and private actors, between&nbsp;countries&nbsp;of&nbsp;different&nbsp;income levels,&nbsp;have the&nbsp;purpose of promoting economic and social&nbsp;progress&nbsp;in the South countries, so&nbsp;it is&nbsp;more balanced&nbsp;and sustainable.in relation to the northern countries.
</p>
<p class="p2">
  Our Foundation&nbsp;sees development&nbsp;as self-development, people is not developed by others ; they,and their cultures and&nbsp;nations, develop&nbsp;themselves.&nbsp;Others&nbsp;can help,&nbsp;encourage, assist,&nbsp;facilitate, but&nbsp;also prevent,&nbsp;hinder,&nbsp;etc..
</p>
<p class="p1">
  We agree&nbsp;on a&nbsp;multidimensional&nbsp;concept&nbsp;of development,&nbsp;whom we can&nbsp;express&nbsp;five major&nbsp;dimensions:
</p>
