<h3 class="p1">
  <span class="s1">Where we intervene</span>
</h3>
<p class="p1">
  We work in <strong>Senegal</strong>, specifically in the neighborhood of <strong>Sam Sam</strong>, located in the district of Diamaguène-SICAP Mbao <strong>Pikine</strong> city, which belongs to the region of <strong>Dakar</strong>. The permanent poverty, economic insecurity and the need to survive day to day, is the only concern of its inhabitants. The lack of education of children and youth, and high unemployment, are one of the reasons why BPDE has chosen to work there.
</p>
